{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-5", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "通往舞會的邀請函", "storyInfo": "在睦的夢境中，保留著原本記憶的睦並沒有選擇離開夢境，而是決定在雷姆必拓當一個普通的小女孩。原本想要勸睦離開的祥子發現睦在這裡的生活比以往任何時候都還幸福，難以抉擇的她決定在睦表演時離席。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g10_dreamcastlestage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我們一同歡笑，我們一同哭泣。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>在華麗的舞台上，上演一齣熱鬧非凡的獨角戲。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>我，毋畏死亡。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g9_warmrabbitnest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥，來，喝下去。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drinkswllw", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喉嚨沒有那麼痛了……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。這個給你，雷姆必拓到處都是沙塵，一定要拿好水袋和護目鏡。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pcket", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子接過睦遞來的物資，她的雙手緊緊地握著它們，鼓脹的水袋好像隨時都會被擠破。"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥，你有點奇怪，是不是不舒服？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒什麼……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，你……還記得我？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得我們經歷過的那些事？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我全都記得。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子感覺自己終於變得冷靜了一點，她開始環顧四周——"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "方才她們順著狹長的礦道一直深入，最終來到了這裡。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡陰暗潮濕，只有油燈和爐火提供著微弱的光亮。"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "床與餐桌之間僅有一人寬的空隙，而從桌上水杯的數量來看，居住在這裡的絕對不只睦一人。"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，你……已經在這裡生活多久了？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一年，也許更久。在這裡需要考慮的事很簡單，時間的流逝也沒有那麼明顯。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……你對時間沒有任何感覺，是因為你身處在夢裡。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，你為什麼會做這樣一個夢……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢……？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，我有重要的事和你說。這裡不是現實，我們現在應該——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊呀——小睦，你怎麼現在就回來了？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_runstop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_kneelsnow_s", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 12.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個身影從身後跑了進來，直接將睦撲倒在柔軟的小床上。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽、媽媽，身上有灰，先等一下……", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，都快一天沒見面了，讓我抱一下嘛！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有、有人……", "name": "若葉睦"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#1$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，小祥也在這裡啊！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好久沒來我們家了吧？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "南小姐……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，怎麼這麼見外啦，叫“南”就好了啦。", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我有時也會這麼叫媽媽。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，你和南小姐的關係什麼時候變得這麼好了……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的關係一直都很好啊，畢竟是母女嘛~", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，今天的收穫怎麼樣？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（翻找口袋）今天天氣有點熱，買黃瓜汁的人比平常多一點。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦小心翼翼地將手中的布袋打開，裡面是一些零星的硬幣。"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯——小睦，你好棒！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（翻翻口袋）喏，這是我的。", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#15$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇……媽媽好厲害。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#15$3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼哼，不知道為什麼，今天找我修補衣服的人特別多哦！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你爸爸今天也很努力哦，在工地裡忙了一整天。我送午餐給他的時候，看到他那副灰頭土臉的樣子實在不忍心，就特別允許他收工之後去喝一小杯。", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他現在啊——應該已經一大瓶啤酒下肚了吧！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛好今天小祥來了，機會難得，不如我們請大家一起來吃飯吧！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家能聚在一起吃飯，好開心。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊！而且今天收入不錯，一定要多吃一點！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小祥千萬別客氣！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥，怎麼了？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……沒有……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前這個明顯就不富裕的家，光禿禿的泥巴牆、微弱的油燈……"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼睦的夢裡，會出現這些？"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，還有南……這位是？", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#11$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是我從小認識的朋友，祥。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好~", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#4$2"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來是想問你們，要不要共進晚餐？", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做了很多份，如果你們願意的話，就一起來吧。", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這怎麼好意思呢！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽你們的鄰居說，你們家的煙囪好像幾天都沒動靜了……", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#10$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（摸摸肚子）唔……", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，離上次聚會已經快一個月了吧？", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都很想再聽到小睦的演奏呢。", "name": "溫米"}, "figure_art": "avg_4081_warmy_1#1$2"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的話……小睦，你是怎麼想的呢？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……我嗎？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#5$3"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小祥肯定也很想聽小睦的演奏吧？就算聽了這麼多次，還是百聽不厭呢！", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不介意的話，就在我們家辦聚會吧！其實我們剛剛還在討論要請大家一起來吃飯呢。", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥，你覺得呢？", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得……睦，由你自己來決定吧。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#1$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯，那我願意。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g9_warmrabbitnest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0,