 "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎儀式過後，大家的注意力又重新回到了聚會本身。祥子獨自靠在角落的牆上，眼神複雜地看著眼前的這一切。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "posfrom": "-150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實……我全都知道。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸……？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一切都是假的，南會對我這麼溫柔，都是假的。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這都是——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以見到你的時候，我就知道，自己該回去了。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#14$3"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，給我一個機會吧。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個告別的機會，然後再結束。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至少在這裡，我也想像你們一樣，能自由地歌唱一次。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walk_stage", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "nw"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒等祥子回應，睦抱著吉他，緩緩朝人群走去。"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，你準備好了嗎？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……大家好。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#10$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小睦，你怎麼了？有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……椅子，我的椅子。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#16$3"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經準備好囉。喏，這個椅子，是你常用的那張吧？", "name": "睦的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1939_1#1$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦小心地觀察著那把高腳椅，椅面上布滿了深深的裂紋。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，就是它。", "name": "若葉睦"}, "figure_art": "avg_4183_mortis_1#13$3"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothtrailground", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦緩緩坐下，所有人都跟著放輕了呼吸。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "若葉睦", "content": "接下來，請聆聽……"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "若葉睦", "content": "《春日影》。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i07_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一生都無法忘記的旋律，在睦的夢境中再次被奏響。"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跟記憶裡一樣，此刻睦手中吉他的聲音無比清澈悠揚，溫暖著每一個人。"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的若葉睦，卻讓祥子感到無比陌生。"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她已經不是那個不善於表達自己感情的睦了。"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然她還在努力嘗試學會表達，但她在這裡，似乎很幸福。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“內心滿是憔悴，眼神顫抖不止”", "x": 300.0, "y": 270.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“我在這世界孤獨一人”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“這不斷凋零的春季”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“每年都只予我冰冷”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦，這也是你的願望嗎……", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天她有無數次機會拉睦離開這裡，而且她相信睦一定會跟她走。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而她始終不忍心這麼做。"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為現在的睦，看起來像是發自內心地感到幸福。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人們隨著音樂輕晃著身體，微弱的燭光將他們的影子映在了牆上，就像春日暖陽下搖曳的樹影一般。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而睦坐在椅子上，被所有人包圍著。她閉著雙眼，手在琴弦間來回撥動，輕聲歌唱。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "此刻的她，又在想些什麼呢？"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“令人揪心又惹人憐愛”", "x": 300.0, "y": 230.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“感覺此刻就能夠明白”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“使人幸福又催人痴迷”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“照耀著無法哭泣的我”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“光芒溫柔地攜我同行——”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫名的情緒籠罩在祥子的心頭——"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是欣慰……還是不甘？抑或兩者都有。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的若葉睦，比和自己在一起時還要開心。"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦就這麼認真地獨自坐在椅子上，唱著熟悉的歌。"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "“透過層層雲彩，不斷閃閃發光”", "x": 300.0, "y": 200.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“填滿心靈又滿溢而出”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“臉頰不知不覺，亦在閃閃發光”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“熱淚沾濕了我的面龐”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“你的手為何如此溫暖”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n“求求你，從此再也不要放開——”", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不鬆開手的話——"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睦在這裡找到的幸福就——"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstprun", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "nrun"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "nrun", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "65_i07_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子轉過身，倉皇而逃。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣，消失在夜色中。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}